      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLUE LAKODA (6) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and six placings from 11 starts. Scored by 3.5 lengths last time (20.08) in a Grade 5 over 366m at Capalaba. Looks a key chance on best form. MAJESTIC ETHICS (5) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at this track in Grade 5 company. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. RAPTOR GIRL (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (20.54) in a Grade 5 at Grafton. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Leading chance. TUTA TIMELINE (1) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.",
